overview:
We, “Integree Projects Limited”, established in 1999 are a prominent manufacturer and service provider of Water & Waste Water Treatment, Environment Auditing & Assessment. These products are designed and manufactured by our diligent team of professionals with utmost precision in compliance with industry standards and norms. In order to meet the variegated needs of clients, we offer our products in different sizes and dimensions as per their requirements. Additionally, we render turnkey projects at the clients’ preferred detonation within the committed time.

Our Team: Engineers Quality controllers Skilled & semi-skilled experts R&D professionals Warehousing & packaging experts Sales and marketing professionals

Our Infrastructure: In order to meet the growing needs of customers, we have developed a state-of-the-art infrastructure facility. The infrastructure of our organization spreads over a vast area of land due to which we are capable of executing all the business activities under one roof. For having hassle-free working of all the business tasks, we have installed it with varied advanced machines such as lathe, special purpose and welding that are properly handled by our team of professionals.

Quality Assurance: Since establishment, we pay high attention towards the quality of offered products and services. The products offered by us are developed using excellent quality raw material following industry standards. Moreover, our professionals make sure that the projects undertaken by them are rendered keeping in mind the requirements and specifications of the customers.

Client Satisfaction: We are a client-centric organization, which pay high attention in maximizing the contentment of esteemed patrons. The products and services we offer to the patrons are developed and executed under strict vigilance of experts following international standards.
